Title: KitchenAid Artisan — At the Heart of Home
Author: wavelet-director

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Flour and dough drop into a stainless bowl. A soft cloud of flour rises and settles.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Hands tilt the iconic head of an Empire Red KitchenAid Artisan downward. The locking lever clicks.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

Macro: the spiral dough hook turns, folding glossy dough against the bowl wall in slow, deliberate revolutions.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

A red KitchenAid Artisan sits on a butcher-block counter. Warm window light from camera left. A linen towel drapes nearby.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

A hand lifts a deep-crusted boule from a cast-iron Dutch oven. Steam curls upward.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING

A slice of warm bread on a wood board. A pat of butter slides and melts.

CUT TO:

INT. CARD - DAY

CTA card. The KitchenAid wordmark, a tagline, a button, the URL.

FADE OUT.
